{"tid":616843,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"筆直2000 買後備手機","createTime":"2018-04-04T13:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T07:44:31.000Z","uid":166618,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5cea5df035b96c80fc93adfc901cee2bf9016101","tid":616843,"uid":166618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"暫時借用朋友既 Samsung A8 (2015版, 型號 SM-A8000)<br />\n<br />\n打傳說對決會好疾，行路都chokchok下<br />\n<br />\n入場快則人地開始左30秒，一般慢則都成分鐘，人地都升左2lv了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但都只係後備手機剩係用黎打機，用多幾個月應該會擺埋一邊，所以唔想買太貴，筆直2000<br />\n<br />\n想問下除左小米5plus　有冇咩好選擇可以比起我用緊呢部快？<br />\n<br />\n爬過下文有人話625唔岩打機...我唔係好識，唔知係咪講緊小米塊板果個型號"},{"pid":"0fc7d944f2146bc5cc1935939c055bd8b1b7a0e8","tid":616843,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:35:38.000Z","msg":"俾多少少htc u ultra<br />\n但你要預要插住電打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dc0114f09dcbbc47a23d36fb00c6e01a2c6820","tid":616843,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"nokia 6用630加有4gb ram應該夠做(如果傳説依類普通game嘅話)<br />\nbtw點都唔揀屌米，個ui會越用越拖慢部機，除非你識flash其他rom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b8d7a36d0826270c3210195eab58bd33796dc4","tid":616843,"uid":166618,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0fc7d944f2146bc5cc1935939c055bd8b1b7a0e8","tid":616843,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:35:38.000Z","msg":"俾多少少htc u ultra<br />\n但你要預要插住電打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"超過筆直又會想直接買IPHONE算數...BUT THANKS你意見，我都考慮下"},{"pid":"dc052a067369b84dc64c6dc8c3c541b709cf44ee","tid":616843,"uid":166618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9dc0114f09dcbbc47a23d36fb00c6e01a2c6820","tid":616843,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":